  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ducky Runnerz is a fast-paced 2D precision platformer where you play as a determined mother duckling rescuing her stolen eggs from the malicious raccoon gang!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ducky will leap from walls, dodge spikes, and collect power-ups to help her traverse challenging levels, racing against the clock. Each level has a specific time limit to be completed. If you run out of time, the raccoon gang will take you too.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An epic original soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique platforming challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cutscenes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11 Steam achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A duck!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ducky Runnerz is a fast-paced 2D precision platformer where you play as a determined mother duckling rescuing her stolen eggs from the malicious raccoon gang!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ducky will leap from walls, dodge spikes, and collect power-ups to help her traverse challenging levels, racing against the clock. Each level has a specific time limit to be completed. If you run out of time, the raccoon gang will take you too.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An epic original soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique platforming challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cutscenes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11 Steam achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A duck!</p></li></ul>",
